<h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
<p>Dear {{name}},</p>
<p>Thank you for your order. Your order details are as follows:</p>
<p>Order ID: {{orderId}}</p>
<h2>Order Items:</h2>
<ul>
  {{#each orderItems}}
    <li>{{this.product.name}}
      - Quantity:
      {{this.quantity}}
      - Price: ${{this.price}}</li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
<p>Total: ${{total}}</p>
<p>We will notify you when your order has been shipped.</p>